  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atsibsteet/ ka tas KUNGS\nDeews irr/ wiꞥsch irr muhs dar-\nrijs/ un ne mehs paſchi/ par fa-\nweem Laudim/ un par fawas\nGannibas Awim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ee-eita zaur wiꞥza Wahr-\ntim ar Pateiſchann/ wiꞥna\nPagalmôs ar Teiktchannu/patei-\nzeet wiꞥnam/ flawejeet wiꞥna\nWahrdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS irr labs/\nwiꞥna Schehlastiba paleê muh-\nschigi/ un wiꞥna Pateefiba lihds\nRaddu Raddeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta CI. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Dseefma/ eekſch ka tee Waldneeki\nwarr mahzitees/ fo teem tik labbi preekſch\nfewis buhs darriht: 1/ 2/ 3. Un lahdus\nRunnas.Kungus un Gullainus teem buhs\nturrecht: 4/etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eena Dahwida Dseef-\nma. No Schehlastibas\nun Teefas gribbu es\ndseedaht/ tew KUNGS dseeda-\nfchu es.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es turrohs gudri eekſch\ntahs Nenoseedsibas Zeltu/ kad\nnahkji tu pee mannis? es stai-\ngaju ar skaidru Sirdi manna\nNamina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es ne apneimmohs kahdn\nblehmas Leetu/ es eenihstu to\nPahrkahpschanas Darbu/ ka tee\npee mannim ne paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Niknat Sirdi no mannim\nja-atſtahjabs/ to Launu es ne\neeredſu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas fawu Tuwaku fleppe-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mannas Azzis raaga us\nteem Peetizzigeem eekſch Sem-\nmes/ ka tee pee man paleek/ kas\nus to Nenoseedsibas Zeltu staiga/\nto neinnu es jew par Sullaint.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas Wittibu dsenn/ tas ne\npaleek manna Namná/ tee Mel-\nkuti preekſch mannahm Azzin ne\npastahiv.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Agri nomaitaju es wiſſus\nBesdeewigus tahs Semmes/ ka\nes wiſſus Cannadarritajus no ta\nKUNGA Pilgfahta isdeldu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta CII. Dseefma.\nIrr weenn ſirdiga Luhafchana preekſch wiſſeem\nApbehdinatem/ ka Deems tohs no fawahn\nBehdahm gribbetu isveſtiht/ un pee Zianas/\ntas irr pee tahs Schehlastibas Walstibas/\nka eekſch Kristus apfohlita/ glahbt un ustur,\nreht: 2.ic.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eena Luhgschana tahda\nBehdign/ kad tas irr\napbehdinahts/ un fawu\nSchehloſchanu ta KUNGA\nPreekſcha isgabsch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ak KUNGS! klański\nmannu Luhgschanu/ un lai man-\nna Sauſchana pee tewis nahk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne paslep tawu Waigu\npreekſch man/ atgreestawu Au-\nfi pee man Behdu Laika/ tai\nDeena kad es tauzu/ paklaufi\nmann drihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo mannas Deenas irr iṣ-\nnihkuſchas ka Duhmi/ un manni\nKauli irr tsdegguſcht ka weena\nPagale.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
